tiger lily finished peter pans song while rigbys wound was 
quickly dressed offstage 
it was like the mike tyson fight mccoy said we were 
trying to get our peter pan patched up for round 15 there was 
blood everywhere 
the audience definitely knew peter had been in a tough fight 
