sirens wailed for two minutes throughout israel 
sunday as life briefly came to a standstill in remembrance of the 6 
million jews slain in the nazi holocaust 
as the sirens sounded at 10 am traffic ground to a halt and 
thousands of israelis stood silently at attention to honor the 
victims 
hundreds of israelis also marked holocaust martyrs and heroes 
