the presidents appreciation for whatever roles iran and syria 
played in polhills release 
there were no deals no negotiations with the hostage 
takers said fitzwater we have no way of identifying any 
specific action on our part that could have been a contributing 
factor to the release 
concerning iran which has bedeviled the united states in a 
string of hostage events over the past 10 years fitzwater said 
we do recognize their role we do show some gratitude for any 
help they may have given in this case we continue to indicate that 
this is a course of action that does beget good will 
